- **Triple-to-equation conversion** ŌĆö done by rewriting with `RustM.Triple_iff_BitVec`, normalising via `simp [RustM.toBVRustM]`, then a three-way `cases` on `binomial_u64.binomial n 0`'s outcome (`none` / `ok` / `error`) ŌĆö error case dispatched by `cases e <;> simp`.
